INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("6957","453","_logo_caption","field_551bff0f9b7cc");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("6958","453","lead_paragraph","NovaStar Solutions is a leading provider of new IT hardware and engineering software, IT asset management, and instrument calibration services.");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("6959","453","_lead_paragraph","field_551bfcdd15385");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("6960","453","first_content","Our growth since 1998 is fueled by excellent service resulting in high levels of customer satisfaction.\r\n\r\nLocated in Livonia, MI NovaStar serves automotive, manufacturing, aerospace, medical device, nuclear energy companies, and major universities.  Partnering with HP, Cisco, Sgi, 3DSystems, Dassault and Siemens, our sales team works diligently to ensure our clients receive best-in-class products, service and pricing.\r\n\r\nWe specialize in providing workstations coupled with engineering CAD/CAE software for industrial design and engineering, and services to support them.\r\n\r\nFor many customers, NovaStar manages new IT asset configuration & acquisition, software imaging, delivery, installation, maintenance, repair, tracking & reporting, removal, refurbishing and re-marketing or disposal of IT equipment.   We sustain R2 certification regarding environmentally correct electronic disposal.");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("6961","453","_first_content","field_551bfd57870dc");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("6962","453","second_content","Our business-to-consumer division, Play It Again PCs, helps Novastar capture the value of IT assets at the end of their lifecycle for the banks, leasing companies, Fortune 100 manufacturers and others who look to Novastar for IT Re-Marketing Services. At the same time we provide end users with an excellent source of refurbished IT devices at very competitive prices.\r\n\r\nNovastar’s ISO 17025:2005 certified A2LA accredited calibration laboratory provides a broad scope of instrument calibration services and a unique online customer portal for asset management of measurement instruments.  Discover why nearly 300 companies, government agencies and universities trust their calibration needs to Novastar.\r\n\r\nNovastar is engaged in the communities it serves with participation in Automation Alley, Tech248,  the Society of Manufacturing Engineers (SME), the Society of Automotive Engineers (SAE), the Equipment & Leasing Finance Association (ELFA),  the Livonia Chamber of Commerce, and the University of Michigan Alumni Association.");
