INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("10676","568","_section_2_heading","field_5526af403aaf6");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("10677","568","s2_body","NovaStar knows the value behind I.T. asset recovery. We have helped numerous corporations, organizations, and government agencies recover the value of their used I.T. assets from a variety of situations.\r\n\r\nWe deal in various types of I.T. equipment including personal computers, workstations, tablets, laptops, consumer electronics, servers, projectors, printers, and storage devices\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Merger, Acquisition or Closure</li>\r\n	<li>System Upgrades or Refresh Projects</li>\r\n	<li>End of Life</li>\r\n	<li>Off Rental or Lease</li>\r\n	<li>Customer Returns</li>\r\n	<li>Project Cancellation</li>\r\n	<li>Excess Surplus</li>\r\n</ul>");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("10678","568","_s2_body","field_5526af4b3aaf7");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("10679","568","s3_heading_1","Reverse Logistics");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("10680","568","_s3_heading_1","field_5526b00a3aafa");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("10681","568","s3_body_1","NovaStar’s reverse logistics capabilities help manufacturers, retailers, and third parties recover value of the following:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Customer Returns</li>\r\n	<li>Overstock</li>\r\n	<li>Closeouts / Clearance</li>\r\n	<li>Open Box</li>\r\n	<li>Distressed / Damaged Packaging Goods</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBy marketing direct to the consumer, NovaStar helps its reverse logistics clients maximize recovery value while minimizing costs – i.e. warehousing, auditing, and transportation logistics. And with a zero-landfill policy, every asset has an end point, so rest assured your assets are being handled properly.");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("10682","568","_s3_body_1","field_5526b0403aafc");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("10683","568","s3_heading_2","ITAD Services");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("10684","568","_s3_heading_2","field_5526b0343aafb");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("10685","568","s3_body_2","NovaStar provides a complete, single-source solution that turns our client’s used I.T. assets into cash. Our I.T. Asset Disposition (I.T.A.D.) services include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Warehousing and Inventory Management</li>\r\n	<li>Audit and Testing by Certified Computer Specialists</li>\r\n	<li>High Level Data-Erasure (U.S. Department of Defense DoD 5220.22-M Standards)</li>\r\n	<li>Equipment Appraisal and FMV Price Quotations</li>\r\n	<li>Management and Logistics for De-Installation of Equipment</li>\r\n	<li>Voluntary Surrender Repossession</li>\r\n	<li>Disposal (Environmentally Compliant Recycling – R2 and ISO 14001:2004 Certified)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThese customized I.T.A.D. services are designed to meet the unique requirements of each customer and are created to maximize return on investment (ROI).\r\nLife Cycle Management");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("10686","568","_s3_body_2","field_5526b0503aafd");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("10687","568","s4_heading","Value Add Process");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("10688","568","_s4_heading","field_5526b0bc3aaff");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("10689","568","s4_body","NovaStar can manage the de-installation of your equipment and the logistics from your location to ours from anywhere in the United States. Upon arrival, each asset receives its own unique identification number which is scanned and stored in our database for tracking. Our certified computer technicians then audit, test, and provide high level data erasure for each system. All the equipment is thoroughly cleaned and any and all stickers and tags are removed during this process.\r\n\r\nU.S. Department of Defense (DoD) 5200.22 standard wiping scheme or disk destruction is available upon customer request and certificates of data destruction are provided. The serial numbers of the systems wiped or destroyed are noted on the certificate and signed off on by the technician performing the task. A full report noting system make, model, configuration, and serial number along with condition and functionality are provided to the equipment owner.\r\n\r\nEquipment is securely stored in our warehouse which is equipped with a security system consisting of, but not limited to, video cameras, motion detectors and wired doors and a fire sprinkler system. NovaStar is also fully insured and bonded.");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("10690","568","_s4_body","field_5526b0c53ab00");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("10691","568","s5_heading","Methods of Recovery");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("10692","568","_s5_heading","field_5526b0d93ab02");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("10693","568","s5_body","NovaStar purchases our customers’ used I.T. equipment at fair market wholesale value after testing and auditing. We also offer to sell the equipment on consignment where our customers share in the risk and can benefit from potentially higher resale values. NovaStar can manage employee purchase options and system redeployments too.\r\n\r\nThose customers choosing consignment have the ability to track their inventory. This includes an in-stock view, which reflects the real-time status of client inventory and an inbound history report, which is a historical view in to what equipment was received, when, and from where, all via our secure client portal.\r\n\r\nSustainability is at the core of what NovaStar Solutions does. Our main goal is to retrieve value wherever possible from equipment returned to our facility for remarketing. Over 95% of the equipment sent to us is resold on the secondary market. If a received system is deemed defective and not repairable, NovaStar will harvest the system for its working components, and the rest will be disposed of properly in accordance with local laws and regulations. Because NovaStar is an R2 Certified electronics waste recycler, every I.T. asset has an end point and you can rest assured your asset will not end up in landfill.\r\n\r\nNovaStar requires its downstream electronics waste partners to be R2 Certified and to use EPA approved standards and provide certificates of destruction. Annual audits are conducted of our downstream providers with NovaStar personnel inspecting our waste management partner’s facility.");
