INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("12651","624","_section_2b1","field_551aa1ffab770");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("12652","624","section_2b2","[button type=\"info\" target=\"_blank\" size=\"md\" link=\"/wp-content/uploads/scopepdfOPT.pdf\"]Novastar\'s Accreditation Scope [/button]\r\n\r\nOur American Association for Laboratory Accreditation – A2LA accreditation is something we’re proud to have achieved and gives our clients a strong sense of confidence in our calibration services. Located in Livonia Michigan, Novastar is centrally located to serve our local clients from Detroit to Ann Arbor through Southfield, Troy, Warren and the entire metro Detroit business community. We also serve the Grand Rapids area with weekly pick-ups and deliveries.\r\n<ul class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n	<li>Force up to 500K lbs</li>\r\n	<li>Torque</li>\r\n	<li>Acceleration</li>\r\n	<li>Electrical DC to 18 GHz</li>\r\n	<li>Thermodynamics</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n	<li>Acoustic</li>\r\n	<li>Pressure/Vacuum to 10K PSI</li>\r\n	<li>Dimensional</li>\r\n	<li>Hardness</li>\r\n	<li>PH/Conductivity</li>\r\n	<li>Environmental Chamber</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nNovastar provides maintenance and repair services for most makes and models of shaker tables.\r\n<h4><a title=\"Shaker Service\" href=\"http://192.169.219.222/~novastar/calibration/shaker-service/\">Novastar Shaker Service</a></h4>");
