INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("16930","864","_s2_image","field_5526bad5cdbb8");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("16931","864","s2_body","NovaStar Solutions has helped numerous businesses, corporations, financial institutions, and government agencies recover value in their aging IT assets from a variety of situations including:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Merger, Acquisition or Closure</li>\r\n	<li>System Upgrades or Refresh Projects</li>\r\n	<li>End of Life</li>\r\n	<li>Off Rental or Lease</li>\r\n	<li>Customer Returns</li>\r\n	<li>Project Cancellation</li>\r\n	<li>Excess Surplus</li>\r\n	<li>Reverse Logistics</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhether it’s PCs, laptops, tablets, consumer electronics, printers, servers, or storage, we understand the value in everything IT.  Our unique remarketing program is tailored to suit your needs, ensuring you are receiving the maximum possible value for your equipment.");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("16932","864","_s2_body","field_5526af4b3aaf7");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("16933","864","s3_heading_1","Reverse Logistics");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("16934","864","_s3_heading_1","field_5526b00a3aafa");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("16935","864","s3_body_1","NovaStar’s reverse logistics capabilities help manufacturers, retailers, and third parties recover value of the following:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Customer Returns</li>\r\n	<li>Overstock</li>\r\n	<li>Closeouts / Clearance</li>\r\n	<li>Open Box</li>\r\n	<li>Distressed / Damaged Packaging Goods</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBy marketing direct to the consumer, NovaStar helps its reverse logistics clients maximize recovery value while minimizing costs – i.e. warehousing, auditing, and transportation logistics. And with a zero-landfill policy, every asset has an end point, so rest assured your assets are being handled properly.");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("16936","864","_s3_body_1","field_5526b0403aafc");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("16937","864","s3_heading_2","ITAD Services");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("16938","864","_s3_heading_2","field_5526b0343aafb");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("16939","864","s3_body_2","NovaStar Solutions provides a complete, single-source solution that turns our client’s used IT assets into cash.  Our IT Asset Disposition (ITAD) services include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Warehousing and Inventory Management</li>\r\n	<li>Audit and Testing by Certified Computer Specialists</li>\r\n	<li>Low Level Secure Data Erasure to NIST 800-88 and U.S. Department of Defense DoD 5220.22-M Standards</li>\r\n	<li>Equipment Appraisal and FMV (Fair Market Value) Price Quotations</li>\r\n	<li>Management and Logistics for De-Installation of Equipment</li>\r\n	<li>Voluntary Surrender Repossession</li>\r\n	<li>Environmentally Compliant Disposal (R2 (Responsible Recycling),ISO 14001:2004, and OHSAS 18001:2007 Certified)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThese ITAD services are customized to meet the unique requirements of each customer and are created to maximize return on investment.");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("16940","864","_s3_body_2","field_5526b0503aafd");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("16941","864","s4_heading","Value Add Process");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("16942","864","_s4_heading","field_5526b0bc3aaff");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("16943","864","s4_body","NovaStar Solutions has the ability to manage the de-installation of your equipment and the logistics from your location to ours from anywhere in the United States and Canada. Upon arrival, assets are tracked by serial number, audited for condition, functionality, and value recovery. Equipment is thoroughly cleaned and all non-OEM identifying labels are removed to ensure customer privacy.\r\n\r\nUpon audit completion, typically within 5-10 business days, a full audit report is furnished to the client which includes detailed asset information including serial number, make, model, configuration, condition, functionality, and estimated recovery value. These audit reports can be customized to suit your needs or automated integration requirements.\r\n\r\nEquipment is securely stored in our warehousing facilities which are equipped with security systems consisting of, but not limited to, video surveillance cameras, motion detectors, wired doors, and a fire sprinkler system.  NovaStar Solutions is also fully insured and bonded.");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("16944","864","_s4_body","field_5526b0c53ab00");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("16945","864","s5_heading","Data Erasure");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("16946","864","_s5_heading","field_5526b0d93ab02");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("16947","864","s5_body","NIST 800-88 and U.S. Department of Defense (DoD) 5220.22-M standard low-level wiping and / or data destruction is available upon customer request and certificates of data destruction are provided. The certificate will include the serial numbers of the storage devices wiped or destroyed as well as the system serial number from when they came from (when applicable).");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("16948","864","_s5_body","field_5526b0e03ab03");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("16949","864","s6_heading","Why NovaStar Remarketing? INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("16950","864","_s6_heading","field_5526c0caa1873");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("16951","864","s6_body","Sustainability is at the core of what NovaStar Solutions strives to achieve. Our core focus is to retrieve value wherever possible when remarketing equipment on behalf of our clients. Over 95% of the remarketing equipment processed is resold on the secondary market, ensuring maximum value for your assets. INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("16952","864","_s6_body","field_5526c0dba1874");
