INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("19128","936","_product_section_title","field_55310b1053c44");
INSERT INTO wp_postmeta VALUES("19129","936","section_1","For over 15 years, Novastar has been a valued partner of several US and global companies, plus world-class universities - assisting with the configuration, ordering, storing, imaging, installation, maintenance and asset tracking of tens of thousands of HP workstations, desktops, laptops,  notebooks and tablets.\r\n\r\nBeing in the heart of the Metro Detroit area, we are heavily involved with automotive manufacturers and their Tier I, II and III level suppliers.    Novastar specializes in HP engineering workstations for design and manufacturing.\r\n\r\nHP hardware along with Dassault Systemes and Siemens PLM software offers a best-in-class solution for Computer Aided Design (CAD) and Computer Aided Engineering (CAE).  Combined with our consulting and support services, we offer a complete package – and at a great value.\r\n\r\nWe are your local, flexible partner with the experience and can-do attitude to  meet your requirements for new IT devices.   Whether you need to buy, lease or rent – we work hard to achieve the solution you need.\r\n\r\nNovastar enjoys a long term and close relationship with Hewlett Packard.  Novastar is an HP Gold Partner One volume Reseller, ServiceOne service provider and a system integrator with HP’s Enterprise Group offerings in servers, networks and storage.");
